eMail

The email address field

Note, that since it is Required the form will not be committed without validating first. The name ("mail") is optional, one could also just have stated @Field.

Via ShowCaseAdvancedFormValidation.HostnameValidator a Validator is referenced, which is created for validating that specific field. The Validator referenced here is ShowCaseAdvancedFormValidation.HostnameValidator which is a local class.
